h3cVoiceEntityControl.name: h3cVoiceEntityControl

revisions.description: The initial version of this MIB file.

h3cVoiceEntityControl.contactinfo: Platform Team H3C Technologies Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip: 100085
h3cVoiceEntityControl.description: This MIB file is to provide the definition of voice dial control configuration.

h3cVoEntityCreateTable.name: h3cVoEntityCreateTable
h3cVoEntityCreateTable.description: The table contains the voice entity information that is used to create an ifIndexed row.

h3cVoEntityIndex.name: h3cVoEntityIndex
h3cVoEntityIndex.description: An arbitrary index that uniquely identifies a voice entity.

h3cVoEntityType.name: h3cVoEntityType
h3cVoEntityType.description: Specify the type of voice related encapsulation.

h3cVoEntityRowStatus.name: h3cVoEntityRowStatus
h3cVoEntityRowStatus.description: This object is used to create, delete or modify a row in this table. The h3cVoEntityType object should not be modified once the new row has been created.

h3cVoEntityCommonConfigTable.name: h3cVoEntityCommonConfigTable
h3cVoEntityCommonConfigTable.description: This table contains the general voice entity information.

h3cVoEntityCfgIndex.name: h3cVoEntityCfgIndex
h3cVoEntityCfgIndex.description: An arbitrary index that uniquely identifies a voice entity.

h3cVoEntityCfgCodec1st.name: h3cVoEntityCfgCodec1st
h3cVoEntityCfgCodec1st.description: This object indicates the first desirable CODEC of speech of this dial entity.

h3cVoEntityCfgCodec2nd.name: h3cVoEntityCfgCodec2nd
h3cVoEntityCfgCodec2nd.description: This object indicates the second desirable CODEC of speech of this dial entity.

h3cVoEntityCfgCodec3rd.name: h3cVoEntityCfgCodec3rd
h3cVoEntityCfgCodec3rd.description: This object indicates the third desirable CODEC of speech of this dial entity.

h3cVoEntityCfgCodec4th.name: h3cVoEntityCfgCodec4th
h3cVoEntityCfgCodec4th.description: This object indicates the forth desirable CODEC of speech of this dial entity.

h3cVoEntityCfgDSCP.name: h3cVoEntityCfgDSCP
h3cVoEntityCfgDSCP.description: This object indicates the DSCP(Different Service Code Point) value of voice packets.

h3cVoEntityCfgVADEnable.name: h3cVoEntityCfgVADEnable
h3cVoEntityCfgVADEnable.description: This object indicates whether the VAD(Voice Activity Detection) is enabled.

h3cVoEntityCfgOutbandMode.name: h3cVoEntityCfgOutbandMode
h3cVoEntityCfgOutbandMode.description: This object indicates the DTMF(Dual Tone Multi-Frequency) outband type of this dial entity.

h3cVoEntityCfgFaxLevel.name: h3cVoEntityCfgFaxLevel
h3cVoEntityCfgFaxLevel.description: This object indicates the fax level of this dial entity.

h3cVoEntityCfgFaxBaudrate.name: h3cVoEntityCfgFaxBaudrate
h3cVoEntityCfgFaxBaudrate.description: This object indicates the fax baudrate of this dial entity.

h3cVoEntityCfgFaxLocalTrainPara.name: h3cVoEntityCfgFaxLocalTrainPara
h3cVoEntityCfgFaxLocalTrainPara.description: This object indicates the fax local train threshold of this dial entity.

h3cVoEntityCfgFaxProtocol.name: h3cVoEntityCfgFaxProtocol
h3cVoEntityCfgFaxProtocol.description: This object indicates the fax protocol of this dial entity.

h3cVoEntityCfgFaxHRPackNum.name: h3cVoEntityCfgFaxHRPackNum
h3cVoEntityCfgFaxHRPackNum.description: This object indicates the high speed redundancy packet numbers of t38 and standard-t38.

h3cVoEntityCfgFaxLRPackNum.name: h3cVoEntityCfgFaxLRPackNum
h3cVoEntityCfgFaxLRPackNum.description: This object indicates the low speed redundancy packet numbers of t38 and standard-t38.

h3cVoEntityCfgFaxSendNSFEnable.name: h3cVoEntityCfgFaxSendNSFEnable
h3cVoEntityCfgFaxSendNSFEnable.description: This object indicates whether sends NSF(Non-Standard Faculty) to fax of this dial entity.

h3cVoEntityCfgFaxTrainMode.name: h3cVoEntityCfgFaxTrainMode
h3cVoEntityCfgFaxTrainMode.description: This object indicates the fax train mode of this dial entity.

h3cVoEntityCfgFaxEcm.name: h3cVoEntityCfgFaxEcm
h3cVoEntityCfgFaxEcm.description: This object indicates whether the ECM(Error Correct Mode) is enabled.

h3cVoEntityCfgPriority.name: h3cVoEntityCfgPriority
h3cVoEntityCfgPriority.description: This object indicates the priority of this dial entity.

h3cVoEntityCfgDescription.name: h3cVoEntityCfgDescription
h3cVoEntityCfgDescription.description: This object indicates the textual description of this dial entity.

h3cVoPOTSEntityConfigTable.name: h3cVoPOTSEntityConfigTable
h3cVoPOTSEntityConfigTable.description: This table contains the POTS(Public Switched Telephone Network) entity information.

h3cVoPOTSEntityConfigIndex.name: h3cVoPOTSEntityConfigIndex
h3cVoPOTSEntityConfigIndex.description: An arbitrary index that uniquely identifies a voice entity.

h3cVoPOTSEntityConfigPrefix.name: h3cVoPOTSEntityConfigPrefix
h3cVoPOTSEntityConfigPrefix.description: This object indicates the prefix which is added to the called number.

h3cVoPOTSEntityConfigSubLine.name: h3cVoPOTSEntityConfigSubLine
h3cVoPOTSEntityConfigSubLine.description: This object indicates the voice subscriber line of this dial entity.

h3cVoPOTSEntityConfigSendNum.name: h3cVoPOTSEntityConfigSendNum
h3cVoPOTSEntityConfigSendNum.description: This object indicates the digit of phone number to be sent to the destination. 0..31: Number of digits (that are extracted from the end of a number) to be sent, in the range of 0 to 31. It is not greater than the total number of digits of the called number. 65534: Sends all digits of a called number. 65535: Sends a truncated called number.

h3cVoVoIPEntityConfigTable.name: h3cVoVoIPEntityConfigTable
h3cVoVoIPEntityConfigTable.description: This table contains the VoIP entity information.

h3cVoVoIPEntityCfgIndex.name: h3cVoVoIPEntityCfgIndex
h3cVoVoIPEntityCfgIndex.description: An arbitrary index that uniquely identifies a voice entity.

h3cVoVoIPEntityCfgTargetType.name: h3cVoVoIPEntityCfgTargetType
h3cVoVoIPEntityCfgTargetType.description: This object indicates the type of the session target of this entity.

h3cVoVoIPEntityCfgTargetAddrType.name: h3cVoVoIPEntityCfgTargetAddrType
h3cVoVoIPEntityCfgTargetAddrType.description: The IP address type of object h3cVoVoIPEntityCfgTargetAddr.

h3cVoVoIPEntityCfgTargetAddr.name: h3cVoVoIPEntityCfgTargetAddr
h3cVoVoIPEntityCfgTargetAddr.description: This object indicates the target IP address.

h3cVoEntityNumberTable.name: h3cVoEntityNumberTable
h3cVoEntityNumberTable.description: The table contains the number management information.

h3cVoEntityNumberEntry.name: h3cVoEntityNumberEntry
h3cVoEntityNumberEntry.description: The entry of h3cVoEntityNumberTable. H3cVoEntityIndex is used to uniquely identify these numbers registered on the server. The same value of h3cVoEntityIndex used in the corresponding H3CVoEntityCommonConfigTable is used here.

h3cVoEntityNumberAuthUser.name: h3cVoEntityNumberAuthUser
h3cVoEntityNumberAuthUser.description: This object indicates the username of the entity number to authorize.

h3cVoEntityNumberPasswordType.name: h3cVoEntityNumberPasswordType
h3cVoEntityNumberPasswordType.description: This object indicates the password type of the entity number to authorize. The encrypting type of password: 0 : password simple, means password is clean text. 1 : password cipher, means password is encrypted text. default is 65535.

h3cVoEntityNumberPassword.name: h3cVoEntityNumberPassword
h3cVoEntityNumberPassword.description: This object indicates the password of the entity number to authorize.

h3cVoEntityNumberStatus.name: h3cVoEntityNumberStatus
h3cVoEntityNumberStatus.description: This object indicates the current state of the entity number.

h3cVoEntityNumberExpires.name: h3cVoEntityNumberExpires
h3cVoEntityNumberExpires.description: This is the interval time for entity number updating registered message.
